http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/bangalore/Biker-dies-after-bus-runs-over-him/article14022741.ece

A 22-year-old motorcycle rider was killed on the spot when a BMTC bus ran over him after knocking down his bike on Thanisandra Main road on Tuesday.The deceased Zabiuddin, a resident of Bharat Nagar, was returning home from work. The BMTC bus travelling towards Majestic, knocked down his motorcycle while trying to overtake another vehicle and ran over him after he slipped under the wheels.The Banasawadi traffic police rushed to the spot and arrested the driver. The police also seized the bus.